data.oai_dc:dc: This project is for data collected using the standardised 2 ha Track Plot methodology, in the sandy deserts of inland Australia. For further details of this methodology, see: Moseby, K.E., Nano, T., and Southgate, R. (2009). Tales in the Sand: A guide to identifying arid zone fauna using spoor and other sign. Ecological Horizons, South Australia.|509 occurrences
